(889, '_transient_dash_4077549d03da2e451c8b5f002294ff51', '<div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''https://wordpress.org/news/2015/07/wordpress-4-3-beta-1/''>WordPress 4.3 Beta 1</a> <span class="rss-date">July 2, 2015</span><div class="rssSummary">WordPress 4.3 Beta 1 is now available! This software is still in development, so we don’t recommend you run it on a production site. Consider setting up a test site just to play with the new version. To test WordPress 4.3, try the WordPress Beta Tester plugin (you’ll want “bleeding edge nightlies”). Or you can [&hellip;]</div></li></ul></div><div class="rss-widget"><ul><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://blog.akismet.com/2015/07/06/akismet-3-1-3-wordpress/''>Akismet: Akismet WordPress Plugin 3.1.3</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/jetpack-3-6-adds-the-ability-to-manage-your-connections-to-jetpack''>WPTavern: Jetpack 3.6 Adds the Ability to Manage Your Connections to Jetpack</a></li><li><a class=''rsswidget'' href=''http://wptavern.com/pressnomics-4-set-for-march-3-4-2016-in-phoenix-az''>WPTavern: Pressnomics 4 Set for March 3-4, 2016 in Phoenix, AZ</a></li></ul></div>', 'no'),
